high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the front of the microwave and face it.
Slice the food in the microwave with the knife.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Pick up a slice of food from the microwave.
Turn left, walk to the stove and face it.
Place the sliced food into the pan on the stove.
Pick up the pan from the stove.
Turn around and walk to the center island counter and face it.
Place the pan on to the counter.
anns.task_desc: Slice food in the microwave to be put in the pan on the stove and moved to the center counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk across the room and turn left to face the microwave.
Cut the potato in the microwave into slices.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Pick up a slice of potato from in the microwave.
Turn left and walk forward to face the stove.
Place the potato slice in the pan on the stove.
Pick up the pan with a potato slice in it on the stove.
Turn right and step forward to face the center table in the kitchen.
Place the pan with a potato slice in it on the center table in the kitchen.
anns.task_desc: To put a slice of potato in a pan plus move them to the table in the center of the kitchen.

high_descs: Turn to your left, take two steps forward, turn right to face the counter with a cabbage
Pick up the butter knife by the cabbage from the counter top.
Take the knife and go to the microwave
Open the microwave, cut the apple on the left side in the microwave
Put the knife on the plate inside the microwave
Take a slice of apple out, and close the microwave
Carry the slice and go to the stove
Put the slice on the pan on the stove
Lift the pan from the stove
Turn right twice and go and face the table in the mid-way
Put the pan with slice of the apple on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of apple in the pan and place them on the table
